# Catalog preprocessor output: derived from src/TianWen.Lib/Astrometry/Catalogs/*.json.lz
# via tools/preprocess-catalog.ps1. Built locally by the PreprocessCatalogs MSBuild
# target (pure .NET, no external binaries) and on CI by the `build` job, then shared
# with downstream jobs as the `preprocessed-catalogs` artifact. See PLAN-catalog-binary-format.md.
src/TianWen.Lib/Astrometry/Catalogs/*.gs.gz

# SASP filter/sensor/SED data is produced by tools/import-sasp-data (downloads
# SASP_data.fits from setiastro/setiastrosuitepro on GitHub). Unlike the catalog
# .gs.gz files there's no committed .json.lz source to regenerate from, so these
# three files ARE tracked in git -- exempt from the wildcard above.
!src/TianWen.Lib/Astrometry/Catalogs/filter_curves.gs.gz
!src/TianWen.Lib/Astrometry/Catalogs/sensor_qe.gs.gz
!src/TianWen.Lib/Astrometry/Catalogs/pickles_sed.gs.gz
# Lavapipe min-repro zip (built artifact for upstream bug filing)
LavapipeMinRepro.zip
